ad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qma7d3FzHTSVn2DgE9AbNaLvfRoboKhin32eQMvvqR38Jx?filename=nixvOHH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnixvOHH.jpg&h=5fccf517&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個畫面好似：<br />\n<br />\nStaff：快啲入去喇！屌你！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXqZMAC9dfGWzuzGe2rvt1peEaeKL7nAfc4B89N9d6329?filename=93nWKgh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F93nWKgh.jpg&h=273d5248&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後入返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWEGxHFuEEBBLqtBhZqMpxGU7yQshKmvuGkxz15yConG3?filename=hRyZG3j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhRyZG3j.jpg&h=8aefc585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼續參觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qma7Ppgs7e7AP7b1jcJCbfzG78SRkHpUYaXX7DTQGCwLAc?filename=KgrAfoz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKgrAfoz.jpg&h=95bbca9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRVcg97Vn9qMQHoVgpqk6CfiQSwwofdsty5hVrucynicP?filename=0NzaOJ2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0NzaOJ2.jpg&h=05c1ccae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUKqgdDdsPqgCRdQpHGghfivygeuACwzuhA6uyAzELxzQ?filename=z5v1Vo3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz5v1Vo3.jpg&h=69b1df16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYzBWxuWNXSqye2N4MntQNhxXGmHmbiadk5QucxnXX4VR?filename=WWZidaL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWWZidaL.jpg&h=73721833&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUAY8NTkYZDix28622xcUHa8mB3w7aDsDbrBHh1mY8ppg?filename=sxQxhCs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsxQxhCs.jpg&h=c788c54f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmThMbNBLhddRKWWEdR7Hkmy6kedTxiSwE4VmGjgKnNqet?filename=mGLJpht.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmGLJpht.jpg&h=96015e0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWRLmVTqKG7EBbNX8CLwJQzPJYCXsziwr4DjLwbChedSC?filename=jvcchCv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjvcchCv.jpg&h=c8afefa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbcK3JTMwuDyzua2MU2XgHUCfn3vKXs2amr9ZLmtaU1Qc?filename=1CkhtKb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1CkhtKb.jpg&h=e15c4cfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後入咗架船行咗陣，比啲公仔嚇到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以無影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmagkr1ZFp78gjzsXo3XgbcNMPCxyZnJmXjLFHoSPcQSfY?filename=G1E94hE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG1E94hE.jpg&h=b71ca54d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後去咗搵巴士去高山<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSdL7YvsoRDq47GpipNZ3PBLuPWK38EBFWJx4AGinCagS?filename=BptGaYg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBptGaYg.jpg&h=ad587c26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐足三個鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRSfBZGAdEAs3VRQ66GRhTr8XZsaMzb6vkXrvKBGAevBQ?filename=g4CDdbN.jpg\" data-thumbnai